		       Android Music Player Daemon (aMPD)

MPD running on Android as a Service (on background). Very useful for all
TV-stick running on android.

An Android Service for playing music of various formats.  Music is played
through the android's audio output.  The Service stores info about all
available music, and this info can be easily searched and retrieved. Player
control, info retrieval, and playlist management can all be managed remotely.

For basic installation information see the INSTALL file.

